{"tid":2258291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白羅斯防暴以閃光彈等武力鎮壓示威 逾 200 被捕 反對派號召今日全國大罷工","createTime":"2020-10-26T02:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T02:56:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bda54b24fa7c80485b0a975ab85cd41f3aa123d9","tid":2258291,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T02:31:11.000Z","msg":"白羅斯 8 月大選引發的反政府示威浪潮持續，至少 10 萬民眾響應反對派號召，於當地周日（25日）在首都明斯克示威，抗議選舉舞弊，要求總統盧卡申科下台。防暴警於傍晚以閃光彈、橡膠子彈等武力清場，人權組織指逾 200 人被捕。反對派隨即宣布發動全國大罷工，癱瘓經濟。<br />\n<br />\n白羅斯民眾連續第 11 個周日上街示威。反對派指這次是對盧卡申科政權的最後通牒，要求他立即下台，否則發動人民參加今日（26日）的全國大罷工，癱瘓經濟。<br />\n<br />\n當地媒體估計最少 10 萬人響應。首都明斯克滿街是人，他們叫喊「下台」、「罷工」等口號，朝市中心進發。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E7%99%BD%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E4%BB%A5%E9%96%83%E5%85%89%E5%BD%88%E7%AD%89%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E9%8E%AE%E5%A3%93%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E9%80%BE-200-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B4%BE%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%2599%25BD%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E9%2596%2583%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25BD%2588%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%258E%25AE%25E5%25A3%2593%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-%25E9%2580%25BE-200-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E8%2599%259F%25E5%258F%25AC%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=df9ebe05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%2599%25BD%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E9%2596%2583%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25BD%2588%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%258E%25AE%25E5%25A3%2593%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-%2